    "synopsis": "Hive Fleet Leviathan has been winnowed but never stopped, and now it bears down on Baal itself. Commander Dante recalls every Blood Angel and every successor Chapter he can reach — Flesh Tearers, Blood Drinkers, Lamenters and more — and prepares a defence that no one truly believes will hold. Petitions to Terra return with silence. The Tyranid swarm grinds through void engagements, breaches the fortress-monastery, and threatens to consume the chapter's birthworld for ever. Only when all hope has been spent does another fleet break translation at the system's edge, bearing a banner thought lost for ten thousand years.",
